tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:58:48.000Z","msg":"This joint statement signfies some countries, at least the nordic and netherlands may consider special visa scheme to Hongkongese! Moreover, weapons are blocked from Hongkong colonized by Chinazi！"},{"pid":"453867aa3b5d03c5cb77ab9844fc85f7f89fdbf5","tid":2129692,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"541c92e086e356be2ef18dd40df24f4c7d6b1d9c","tid":2129692,"uid":87433,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"啲英文有啲深 有冇翻譯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:59:14.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔算深喎"},{"pid":"93253402793c3ab2e34056d280c8db552a6fbaba","tid":2129692,"uid":363016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"541c92e086e356be2ef18dd40df24f4c7d6b1d9c","tid":2129692,"uid":87433,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"啲英文有啲深 有冇翻譯？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"google translate more accurate, please!"},{"pid":"1b139b75e7a990e71cb402e8e28617dcda24de4e","tid":2129692,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"453867aa3b5d03c5cb77ab9844fc85f7f89fdbf5","tid":2129692,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"541c92e086e356be2ef18dd40df24f4c7d6b1d9c","tid":2129692,"uid":87433,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"啲英文有啲深 有冇翻譯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:59:14.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔算深喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:59:42.000Z","msg":"google translate<br />\n<br />\n香港：安理會對國家安全法表示嚴重關注<br />\n<br />\n在2020年7月13日在外交事務委員會進行初步討論後，安理會今天通過了結論，對中國全國人大常委會於2020年6月30日通過的香港國家安全立法表示嚴重關切。<br />\n<br />\n這些結論重申了歐盟對&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;原則下香港高度自治的支持，以及它對香港人民的聲援，同時在各個領域制定了一套協調一致的措施。<br />\n<br />\n其中包括：<br />\n<br />\n庇護，移民，簽證和居住政策；<br />\n在香港出口最終使用的特定敏感設備和技術；<br />\n涉及香港學生和大學的獎學金和學術交流；<br />\n對民間社會的支持；<br />\n成員國與香港的引渡安排和其他相關協議的運作<br />\n最後，結論要求在年底之前審查國家安全法的執行情況以及歐盟應對措施的影響。"},{"pid":"794293c2dc0e5f2ca52fbdad2f00c350dd2686db","tid":2129692,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"faf3d5354050e7118693c4765b1b6ceb8cf292fb","tid":2129692,"uid":363016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2b48814f0f3b05a7fa65af8e2d4d91af670d0c45","tid":2129692,"uid":61161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:56:02.000Z","msg":"關注姐係無用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:58:48.000Z","msg":"This joint statement signfies some countries, at least the nordic and netherlands may consider special visa scheme to Hongkongese! Moreover, weapons are blocked from Hongkong colonized by Chinazi！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"以後淨係可以用國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb073dcaf62806dfae10ce6448a491f7a445c906","tid":2129692,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2347a15d35651bd7897fae57de7d2d26628d49fb","tid":2129692,"uid":90601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:01:54.000Z","msg":"Further scrutinising and limiting exports of specific sensitive equipment and technologies for end-use in Hong Kong, in particular where there are grounds to suspect undesirable use relating to internal repression, the interception of internal communications or cybersurveillance;<br />\n<br />\nReviewing the implications of the national security legislation on the operation of Member States&rsquo; extradition and other relevant agreements with Hong Kong;<br />\n<br />\n好快睇左睇 依兩點比較強硬<br />\n<br />\nExploring possibilities for stepping up and coordinating scholarships and academic exchanges involving Hong Kong students and universities;<br />\n<br />\n依點都重要 起碼唔好屈係香港埋19學店度"},{"pid":"b136ca3bc3091c02